# The Seed is a text-only repository. Pin every text file to LF on checkout so byte-exact
# machinery holds on any platform — notably the generated-artifact gate
# (.seed/checks/validate-generated.ts), which compares a committed docs/generated/ artifact
# byte-for-byte against an LF-only regeneration. Without this, a Windows checkout with
# core.autocrlf=true would materialize the artifact as CRLF and fail the gate on a pristine
# tree, with `npm run generate` unable to fix it. Ring 0020.
* text=auto eol=lf
